WEBVTT

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:10.500
‐ ( crowd yelling )
‐ ( Nanbu gasping )

00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:13.500
Crowd: YURI! YURI! YURI! YURI!

00:00:13.500 --> 00:00:16.333
Referee: THREE‐MINUTE ROUNDS!
NO ROUND LIMIT!

00:00:16.333 --> 00:00:19.166
WILL JUNK DOG BE
ANY CHALLENGE AT ALL

00:00:19.166 --> 00:00:21.666
FOR THE UNSTOPPABLE CHAMPION?

00:00:21.666 --> 00:00:24.433
Crowd: YURI! ( yelling )

00:00:24.433 --> 00:00:26.666
Bookie: HEY!
SPECIAL BONUS ROUND HERE!

00:00:29.133 --> 00:00:31.766
Junk Dog: BUT I WANT
TO BELIEVE IN MYSELF,

00:00:31.766 --> 00:00:34.966
BELIEVE THAT MY FAITH
IN MYSELF IS REAL.

00:00:34.966 --> 00:00:36.633
( Nanbu grumbles )

00:00:36.633 --> 00:00:40.000
‐ THIS ISN'T SOME GAME, KID.
‐ Crowd: YURI! YURI!

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:41.533
Nanbu: PLEASE,
YOU GOTTA STOP THIS.

00:00:41.533 --> 00:00:44.000
ODDS THIS BAD
CAN'T MAKE FOR GOOD GAMBLING.

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:47.666
Domoto: TOO LATE FOR THAT.
THE BOSS SAYS TO LET IT HAPPEN.

00:00:47.666 --> 00:00:51.633
BESIDES, NO UNDERGROUND FIGHT
HAS EVER BEEN THIS BIG.

00:00:51.633 --> 00:00:54.900
WHO'D BE DUMB ENOUGH
TO PULL THE PLUG ON THIS?

00:00:54.900 --> 00:00:56.333
( Nanbu grumbles )

00:00:56.333 --> 00:00:58.433
‐ Crowd: YURI! YURI! YURI!
‐ Nanbu: KID, LISTEN!

00:00:58.433 --> 00:01:01.340
WHEN YOU GET THE CHANCE,
TAKE A DIVE, AND COUNT TO TEN...

00:01:02.973 --> 00:01:05.540
OR ELSE YOU'RE DEAD.

00:01:05.540 --> 00:01:07.406
Crowd: YURI! YURI!

00:01:07.406 --> 00:01:09.439
Yuri: ALL RIGHT, KID,
TELL ME YOUR NAME.

00:01:09.439 --> 00:01:11.906
THEY CAN'T PUT YOUR RING NAME
ON A TOMBSTONE.

00:01:11.906 --> 00:01:13.106
( Junk Dog scoffs )

00:01:13.106 --> 00:01:16.273
NO ONE MAKES TOMBSTONES
FOR STRAY DOGS.

00:01:16.273 --> 00:01:18.106
‐ ( bell rings )
‐ ( crowd cheering )

00:01:23.540 --> 00:01:25.506
( Gear whirring )

00:01:25.506 --> 00:01:26.573
( yells )

00:01:27.773 --> 00:01:28.973
( gasps )

00:01:28.973 --> 00:01:31.340
♪

00:01:36.973 --> 00:01:39.473
( Nanbu grumbles )
STOPPED WITH ONE PUNCH.

00:01:39.473 --> 00:01:40.640
( Gear hums )

00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:42.273
THAT'S A HELL OF A JAB.

00:01:42.273 --> 00:01:44.240
IF IT'D HAVE BEEN
A CLEAN HIT, THEN...

00:01:46.606 --> 00:01:48.473
( Junk Dog sighs )

00:01:48.473 --> 00:01:50.040
‐ HMM.
‐ ( Yuri chuckles )

00:01:50.040 --> 00:01:52.506
HOW ABOUT A HANDICAP?

00:01:52.506 --> 00:01:53.273
Junk Dog: HMM?

00:01:54.473 --> 00:01:57.206
Yuri: I'M NOT GONNA
USE MY RIGHT ARM.

00:01:57.206 --> 00:01:59.440
MY LEFT SHOULD BE
ENOUGH FOR YOU.

00:01:59.440 --> 00:02:01.646
‐ ( crowd murmuring )
‐ Man: WHAT'S GOING ON?

00:02:01.646 --> 00:02:04.746
Man #2: HE'S SAYING HE CAN
BEAT HIM WITH JUST ONE HAND.

00:02:04.746 --> 00:02:06.946
( Nanbu growls )

00:02:06.946 --> 00:02:09.680
Junk Dog: WOW.
YOU REALLY ARE GENEROUS.

00:02:09.680 --> 00:02:12.246
THANKS, CHAMP.

00:02:12.246 --> 00:02:14.346
HERE'S HOPING
YOU DON'T REGRET IT.

00:02:21.280 --> 00:02:22.880
HE'S CHANGING
THE ANGLE OF HIS JABS

00:02:22.880 --> 00:02:24.280
TO SHUT DOWN MY PUNCHES.

00:02:25.746 --> 00:02:27.280
LET'S SEE HOW YOU LIKE THIS.

00:02:32.113 --> 00:02:33.880
‐ ( Nanbu chuckles )
‐ Junk Dog: GOT YOU.

00:02:33.880 --> 00:02:36.113
‐ ( Yuri gasps )
‐ ( Junk Dog gasps )

00:02:39.313 --> 00:02:40.280
‐ ( crowd roaring )
‐ ( Nanbu gasps )

00:02:44.180 --> 00:02:46.513
Referee: JUNK DOG IS DOWN!
HE'S DOWN!

00:02:46.513 --> 00:02:47.780
Computer: ONE...

00:02:47.780 --> 00:02:51.080
Nanbu: DAMN, HE WASN'T
BLUFFING ABOUT THAT HANDICAP.

00:02:51.080 --> 00:02:52.346
‐ Computer: THREE...
‐ Nanbu: HE REALLY DID

00:02:52.346 --> 00:02:54.313
TAKE HIM DOWN
WITH JUST A SINGLE HAND.

00:02:54.313 --> 00:02:54.980
‐ Computer: FOUR...
‐ ( Nanbu gasps )

00:02:54.980 --> 00:02:56.746
PARTNER, JUST STAY DOWN!

00:02:56.746 --> 00:02:58.346
YOU'VE DONE ENOUGH IN THERE!

00:02:58.346 --> 00:03:01.320
YOU'RE SERIOUSLY GONNA END UP
DEAD IF YOU KEEP FIGHTING!

00:03:01.320 --> 00:03:02.820
‐ Computer: SEVEN...
‐ ( Junk Dog scoffs )

00:03:02.820 --> 00:03:05.320
DYING DOESN'T BOTHER ME,

00:03:05.320 --> 00:03:08.053
NOT WHEN I'M HAVING
THIS MUCH FUN.

00:03:09.820 --> 00:03:11.586
( sniffs )

00:03:11.586 --> 00:03:14.520
NO WAY AM I GONNA QUIT NOW.

00:03:14.520 --> 00:03:16.220
♪

00:03:27.820 --> 00:03:30.220
( singing in Japanese )

00:04:46.626 --> 00:04:48.160
( crowd cheering )

00:04:50.393 --> 00:04:52.793
( Gear humming )

00:04:54.460 --> 00:04:57.126
( Junk Dog thinking )
THAT SMUG LOOK ON YOUR FACE

00:04:57.126 --> 00:04:58.860
IS STARTING TO PISS ME OFF.

00:04:58.860 --> 00:05:00.233
( Gear whirs )

00:05:04.933 --> 00:05:07.433
( Yuri gasps )

00:05:07.433 --> 00:05:08.966
( crowd roaring )

00:05:13.100 --> 00:05:15.266
Junk Dog: IF YOU'D
JUST USED ONE ARM,

00:05:15.266 --> 00:05:18.166
IT'D BE SLEEPY‐TIME
FOR YOU RIGHT NOW.

00:05:18.166 --> 00:05:20.266
‐ ( Nanbu laughs )
‐ ( crowd murmuring )

00:05:22.900 --> 00:05:24.133
Yuri: HMPH.

00:05:24.133 --> 00:05:25.800
Junk Dog:
ENOUGH WITH THE SHOWBOATING

00:05:25.800 --> 00:05:27.433
AND GRANDSTANDING. FROM NOW ON,

00:05:27.433 --> 00:05:30.133
LET'S FIGHT ON EVEN GROUND,
FAIR AND SQUARE.

00:05:30.133 --> 00:05:34.066
Yuri: RIGHT.
TIME TO DO WHAT YOU ASKED

00:05:34.066 --> 00:05:36.666
AND TEACH YOU
REAL MEGALO‐BOXING.

00:05:36.666 --> 00:05:38.733
( Junk Dog gasps )

00:05:38.733 --> 00:05:39.900
( chuckles )

00:05:39.900 --> 00:05:42.233
THAT'S WHAT I'M TALKING ABOUT.

00:05:42.233 --> 00:05:44.033
♪

00:05:52.733 --> 00:05:55.133
Nanbu: DON'T GET COCKY, KID!

00:05:55.133 --> 00:05:57.866
STAY AWAY FROM HIM!
USE YOUR FOOTWORK!

00:06:05.606 --> 00:06:06.906
( growls )

00:06:13.240 --> 00:06:15.040
Junk Dog: I SEE
WHAT YOU'RE DOING.

00:06:19.606 --> 00:06:21.073
( gasps )

00:06:27.506 --> 00:06:28.106
( Nanbu gasps )

00:06:40.173 --> 00:06:42.373
‐ ( thump )
‐ ( crowd cheering )

00:06:44.073 --> 00:06:46.040
‐ ( Junk Dog gasping )
‐ Computer: ONE...

00:06:47.306 --> 00:06:48.273
TWO...

00:06:50.373 --> 00:06:52.040
THREE...

00:06:53.606 --> 00:06:55.673
Referee: UH, CHAMP, WAIT.

00:06:55.673 --> 00:06:58.240
‐ Yuri: IT'S OVER.
‐ Computer: FIVE...

00:06:58.240 --> 00:07:00.346
Yuri: HE'S NOT GETTING UP
AFTER THAT.

00:07:01.680 --> 00:07:03.713
Computer: SIX...

00:07:03.713 --> 00:07:05.946
Nanbu: THAT'S ENOUGH! STAY DOWN!

00:07:05.946 --> 00:07:08.046
STAY THE HELL DOWN!
STOP BEING...

00:07:08.046 --> 00:07:11.446
Junk Dog: ENOUGH.
GIVE IT A REST, POPS.

00:07:11.446 --> 00:07:14.113
THAT'S NOT WHAT I WANNA HEAR.

00:07:14.113 --> 00:07:15.946
Nanbu: FOR ONCE IN YOUR LIFE,
LISTEN TO ME!

00:07:15.946 --> 00:07:17.946
STAY ON THE MAT!
DON'T GET BACK UP!

00:07:17.946 --> 00:07:19.146
‐ Computer: TEN.
‐ ( bell rings )

00:07:19.146 --> 00:07:20.846
Referee:
K.O. IN THE FIRST ROUND!

00:07:20.846 --> 00:07:23.546
THE WINNER IS YURI!

00:07:23.546 --> 00:07:24.746
( crowd cheering )

00:07:24.746 --> 00:07:26.913
Yuri: SORRY FOR INTERRUPTING
YOUR OPERATION.

00:07:26.913 --> 00:07:28.280
Domoto: GETTING TO WATCH
THE CHAMP FIGHT

00:07:28.280 --> 00:07:31.613
AT NO EXTRA COST,
IF YOU ASK ME, THAT'S A BARGAIN.

00:07:31.613 --> 00:07:35.580
Crowd: YURI! YURI! YURI! YURI!

00:07:35.580 --> 00:07:39.580
YURI! YURI! YURI! YURI!

00:07:39.580 --> 00:07:42.613
YURI! YURI! YURI!

00:07:42.613 --> 00:07:44.946
Junk Dog: SO THAT'S IT?

00:07:44.946 --> 00:07:47.480
THAT'S YOUR
"REAL MEGALO‐BOXING"?

00:07:47.480 --> 00:07:49.280
♪

00:07:53.080 --> 00:07:54.913
( scoffs )

00:07:54.913 --> 00:07:57.146
I'VE GOTTA SAY
I'M NOT IMPRESSED.

00:07:57.146 --> 00:08:01.186
IT COULDN'T EVEN PUT DOWN
A SINGLE STRAY DOG.

00:08:01.186 --> 00:08:04.253
( sighs )
LET'S KEEP THIS MATCH GOING.

00:08:04.253 --> 00:08:07.586
I AIN'T DONE WITH YOU,
NOT BY A LONG SHOT.

00:08:09.520 --> 00:08:11.986
( Nanbu grunts )
THAT'S NOT HAPPENING.

00:08:11.986 --> 00:08:14.086
YOU ALREADY LOST. GET OVER IT.

00:08:14.086 --> 00:08:16.886
( laughs ) COME ON, CHAMP.
GIVE HIM A BREAK.

00:08:16.886 --> 00:08:19.286
LOOK, THE KID DOESN'T KNOW
WHAT HE'S SAYING, OKAY?

00:08:19.286 --> 00:08:21.620
HE'S JUST A HOPELESS DREAMER
THAT THINKS HE CAN‐‐

00:08:21.620 --> 00:08:23.286
Yuri: WE'RE FINISHED HERE.

00:08:23.286 --> 00:08:27.686
I HAVE NOTHING TO PROVE BY
CONTINUING TO FIGHT STRAY DOGS.

00:08:27.686 --> 00:08:30.153
THIS MAY BE YOUR RING,
BUT IT ISN'T MINE.

00:08:30.153 --> 00:08:33.053
( Junk Dog scoffs )
SO NOW THAT BOTHERS YOU, HUH?

00:08:35.686 --> 00:08:37.053
( Yuri chuckles )

00:08:37.053 --> 00:08:40.553
IF YOU'RE REALLY SERIOUS
ABOUT FIGHTING ME AGAIN,

00:08:40.553 --> 00:08:42.486
THEN YOU COME TO ME...

00:08:42.486 --> 00:08:43.486
( Junk Dog gasps )

00:08:43.486 --> 00:08:45.820
Yuri: IN MY RING.

00:08:48.653 --> 00:08:51.520
Junk Dog: WAIT! HOLD IT!

00:08:51.520 --> 00:08:54.386
STOP! YOU GET BACK HERE!

00:08:54.386 --> 00:08:56.220
( echoing ) HEY!

00:09:06.160 --> 00:09:08.126
( engine roaring )

00:09:30.926 --> 00:09:31.893
( gasps )

00:09:38.993 --> 00:09:40.826
( sighs )

00:09:43.426 --> 00:09:46.893
I CAN'T GO BACK TO THAT LIFE.

00:09:46.893 --> 00:09:49.060
( sighs )

00:09:49.060 --> 00:09:50.460
( chuckles )

00:09:56.593 --> 00:09:59.293
NOT AFTER HE SHOWED ME
WHAT'S OUT THERE.

00:09:59.293 --> 00:10:01.200
( roars )

00:10:01.200 --> 00:10:03.066
( thunder rumbles )

00:10:10.266 --> 00:10:12.033
( scraping )

00:10:13.533 --> 00:10:15.166
Yuri: YOU WANT OUT?

00:10:18.300 --> 00:10:20.166
( dog barks )

00:10:26.400 --> 00:10:27.700
( paws tapping )

00:10:27.700 --> 00:10:30.333
( whimpers, barks )

00:10:30.333 --> 00:10:31.500
BOSS.

00:10:35.500 --> 00:10:39.266
Yukiko: I HEAR YOU WENT TO SEE
THAT MAN WITH THE MOTORCYCLE?

00:10:39.266 --> 00:10:40.066
Yuri: I DID.

00:10:40.066 --> 00:10:41.900
Yukiko: YOU MUST
REMEMBER YOUR PLACE

00:10:41.900 --> 00:10:43.900
IN THE GRAND SCHEME
OF THIS ORGANIZATION.

00:10:43.900 --> 00:10:46.933
YOU WON'T STEP INTO THE RING
AGAIN WITHOUT MY PERMISSION.

00:10:46.933 --> 00:10:49.500
FIGHTING IN UNSANCTIONED BOUTS
AT THIS STAGE

00:10:49.500 --> 00:10:51.066
SIMPLY CANNOT BE ALLOWED.

00:10:51.066 --> 00:10:53.066
Yuri: I UNDERSTAND.

00:10:53.066 --> 00:10:56.733
I WILL NEVER INVOLVE MYSELF
WITH THAT MAN AGAIN.

00:10:56.733 --> 00:10:59.133
♪

00:11:02.540 --> 00:11:04.440
Yukiko: I'M GLAD TO HEAR THAT.

00:11:04.440 --> 00:11:08.340
YOUR BODY IS
THE FUTURE OF THIS COMPANY.

00:11:08.340 --> 00:11:10.740
Yuri: YES, I KNOW.

00:11:22.173 --> 00:11:24.840
( clicking )

00:11:24.840 --> 00:11:26.740
♪

00:11:36.173 --> 00:11:37.573
Rapper: ♪♪ UNH, YO

00:11:37.573 --> 00:11:39.740
( rapping in Japanese )

00:12:32.246 --> 00:12:34.246
( song fades )

00:12:34.246 --> 00:12:37.980
Domoto: ALL RIGHT, TONIGHT
WE'RE BACK TO BUSINESS AS USUAL.

00:12:37.980 --> 00:12:39.280
( Nanbu laughs )

00:12:39.280 --> 00:12:40.980
DON'T WORRY.
WE KNOW WHAT TO DO.

00:12:40.980 --> 00:12:43.713
Domoto: GOOD. YOU EXPLAINED
THE SETUP TO YOUR FIGHTER?

00:12:43.713 --> 00:12:45.446
Nanbu: YEAH, HE'S GOT IT.

00:12:46.480 --> 00:12:47.980
HEY THERE, PARTNER.

00:12:47.980 --> 00:12:50.513
EVERYTHING IS ALL SET
FOR THE MATCH.

00:12:50.513 --> 00:12:52.346
MIDDLE OF THE FIFTH ROUND,

00:12:52.346 --> 00:12:54.046
THE OTHER GUY
LANDS A LUCKY PUNCH,

00:12:54.046 --> 00:12:55.746
YOU GO DOWN. PIECE OF CAKE.

00:12:56.946 --> 00:12:59.753
Junk Dog: LISTEN, POPS.
I NEED A FAVOR.

00:12:59.753 --> 00:13:01.586
Nanbu: HUH?

00:13:01.586 --> 00:13:04.420
SURE. WHATEVER YOU NEED.
( laughs )

00:13:04.420 --> 00:13:07.553
THAT SCRAP YOU WERE IN WITH YURI
GAVE THINGS A BOOST.

00:13:07.553 --> 00:13:09.820
IT DOUBLED THE AUDIENCE,
ALONG WITH OUR CUT.

00:13:09.820 --> 00:13:11.820
IF THINGS KEEP GOIN'
THE WAY THEY'RE HEADED NOW,

00:13:11.820 --> 00:13:15.953
I'LL BE OUT OF DEBT
IN NO TIME AT‐‐HMM? WHAT'S THIS?

00:13:15.953 --> 00:13:20.153
Junk Dog: I GOTTA HAVE
ANOTHER SHOT AT FIGHTING YURI.

00:13:20.153 --> 00:13:21.653
GET ME INTO MEGALONIA.

00:13:22.886 --> 00:13:24.920
( Nanbu growls )

00:13:24.920 --> 00:13:26.520
YOU SERIOUS?

00:13:26.520 --> 00:13:29.320
Junk Dog: YEAH. DEAD SERIOUS.

00:13:29.320 --> 00:13:31.453
PLEASE GET ME IN HIS RING.

00:13:31.453 --> 00:13:33.253
( Nanbu chuckles )

00:13:33.253 --> 00:13:35.320
HAVE YOU GONE INSANE?!

00:13:35.320 --> 00:13:36.986
DON'T YOU GET IT?

00:13:36.986 --> 00:13:40.120
HE COULD HAVE TURNED YOU
INTO BLOOD SAUSAGE LAST TIME.

00:13:40.120 --> 00:13:42.086
NOW YOU WANNA TALK
LIKE A BIG SHOT

00:13:42.086 --> 00:13:43.320
AND STEP INTO "HIS RING."

00:13:43.320 --> 00:13:44.686
YOU'RE DELUSIONAL.

00:13:44.686 --> 00:13:46.786
YOU THINK A FRAUD
CAN BECOME THE REAL DEAL.

00:13:46.786 --> 00:13:49.653
Junk Dog: YOU'RE NOT THE ONE
WHO'D BE FIGHTING HIM, POPS.

00:13:49.653 --> 00:13:50.453
I AM.

00:13:51.453 --> 00:13:52.920
( Nanbu groans )

00:13:52.920 --> 00:13:55.786
AW, COME ON.
SNAP OUT OF IT, PARTNER.

00:13:55.786 --> 00:13:58.820
DID YOU FORGET
THAT YOU NEED A CITIZEN I. D.

00:13:58.820 --> 00:14:01.260
TO EVEN ENTER
A SANCTIONED MATCH?

00:14:01.260 --> 00:14:03.260
YOU GOT ONE OF THOSE THINGS?

00:14:03.260 --> 00:14:04.993
NO, I DON'T BELIEVE YOU DO.

00:14:04.993 --> 00:14:07.426
AND EVEN IF YOU DID
HAPPEN TO HAVE ONE,

00:14:07.426 --> 00:14:11.526
ONLY THE TOP FOUR RANKED
FIGHTERS GET INTO THE BRACKET.

00:14:11.526 --> 00:14:13.826
YOU COULD BUST YOUR ASS
LIKE NEVER BEFORE,

00:14:13.826 --> 00:14:16.160
AND YOU'D STILL NEVER GET
THAT FAR IN THREE MONTHS.

00:14:16.160 --> 00:14:18.493
THERE'S JUST NO WAY.

00:14:18.493 --> 00:14:20.760
LISTEN. GUYS LIKE US,

00:14:20.760 --> 00:14:23.826
WE DON'T GET TO THINK
ABOUT TOMORROW.

00:14:23.826 --> 00:14:25.560
YOU FOCUS TOO MUCH
ON THAT STUFF,

00:14:25.560 --> 00:14:28.760
AND YOU END UP A DEAD MAN.

00:14:30.993 --> 00:14:32.626
( laughs )

00:14:32.626 --> 00:14:35.760
ENOUGH WITH ALL THIS
HEAD‐IN‐THE‐CLOUDS CRAP.

00:14:35.760 --> 00:14:38.026
ALL YOU NEED TO DO
IS FOCUS ON THE JOB

00:14:38.026 --> 00:14:40.826
THAT YOU'RE DOING TODAY. GOT IT?

00:14:40.826 --> 00:14:41.760
( chuckles )

00:14:41.760 --> 00:14:43.593
ALL RIGHT, THEN.

00:14:43.593 --> 00:14:46.293
THINK I'M GONNA GO
CHECK THE CROWD NUMBERS.

00:14:46.293 --> 00:14:48.393
GO AHEAD,
AND START GETTING READY.

00:14:48.393 --> 00:14:51.193
( humming a tune )

00:14:53.126 --> 00:14:54.926
( crowd murmuring )

00:14:58.726 --> 00:15:02.366
Referee: THE FIRST MATCH
OF THE DAY IS ABOUT TO BEGIN.

00:15:02.366 --> 00:15:04.100
Nanbu: TAKE A LOOK.

00:15:04.100 --> 00:15:06.166
DAMN, WHAT A BUNCH OF MARKS.

00:15:06.166 --> 00:15:07.733
READY, PARTNER?

00:15:07.733 --> 00:15:10.100
GO A LITTLE EASY
ON THE GUY, OKAY?

00:15:10.100 --> 00:15:12.133
IF YOU GO IN GUNS A‐BLAZIN',

00:15:12.133 --> 00:15:14.600
HE WON'T LAST UNTIL ROUND FIVE.

00:15:14.600 --> 00:15:17.500
HEY! ARE YOU LISTENING
TO ME IN THERE, KID?

00:15:18.800 --> 00:15:19.800
( gasps )

00:15:19.800 --> 00:15:21.333
‐ WHERE'S THE EARPIECE?
‐ ( bell rings )

00:15:21.333 --> 00:15:22.766
( crowd cheering )

00:15:25.066 --> 00:15:26.033
( Rainy chuckles )

00:15:26.033 --> 00:15:28.133
HOLD ON. WHAT ARE YOU...

00:15:30.566 --> 00:15:32.400
( all gasping )

00:15:32.400 --> 00:15:34.333
Referee: UH, START COUNTING.

00:15:34.333 --> 00:15:35.400
Computer: ONE...

00:15:37.100 --> 00:15:37.966
TWO...

00:15:37.966 --> 00:15:39.500
( Nanbu growls )

00:15:39.500 --> 00:15:41.000
‐ UNGRATEFUL BASTARD!
‐ Computer: THREE...

00:15:41.000 --> 00:15:42.366
FOUR...

00:15:42.366 --> 00:15:43.933
Nanbu: WILL YOU BUZZ OFF?!

00:15:43.933 --> 00:15:46.500
‐ I'M IN THE MIDDLE OF‐‐
‐ Computer: FIVE...

00:15:46.500 --> 00:15:48.133
SIX...

00:15:48.966 --> 00:15:51.600
( Nanbu gasps )

00:15:56.733 --> 00:15:58.600
( thumping, whooshing )

00:16:04.640 --> 00:16:05.406
( bubbling )

00:16:05.406 --> 00:16:07.506
( thumping, whooshing continue )

00:16:07.506 --> 00:16:10.340
( man screams )

00:16:10.340 --> 00:16:11.940
( Nanbu shuddering )

