Nanbu: OH.

00:16:49.573 --> 00:16:52.373
Fujimaki: IF YOU REALLY
TAKE YOUR TIME BOILING IT,

00:16:52.373 --> 00:16:57.140
YOU CAN GET 500 GRAMS OF FOND
OUT OF 500 GRAMS OF BONE.

00:16:58.373 --> 00:17:00.580
WORKS OUT PRETTY NICELY,
