( Nanbu stammering )

00:17:01.913 --> 00:17:04.080
( man screams )

00:17:04.080 --> 00:17:05.780
Fujimaki: TELL ME, NANBU,

00:17:05.780 --> 00:17:07.313
HOW MUCH DO YOU WEIGH?

00:17:07.313 --> 00:17:09.113
( Nanbu gasping )

00:17:09.113 --> 00:17:11.446
Fujimaki:
I'M ASKING YOUR WEIGHT.

00:17:11.446 --> 00:17:12.780
SO HOW MUCH?

00:17:12.780 --> 00:17:13.846
( Nanbu stammering )

