( slams head )

00:17:43.413 --> 00:17:45.913
PLEASE, MR. FUJIMAKI,
I'M BEGGING YOU.

00:17:45.913 --> 00:17:47.446
I'LL FIND A WAY
TO PAY YOU BACK.

00:17:47.446 --> 00:17:50.146
I JUST NEED A LITTLE MORE TIME!
I SWEAR TO GOD!

00:17:50.146 --> 00:17:53.146
Fujimaki: I SEE.
IS THAT YOUR ANSWER?

00:17:53.146 --> 00:17:56.546
Nanbu: JUST GIVE ME A CHANCE.

00:17:56.546 --> 00:17:58.313
( shuddering )

00:18:01.753 --> 00:18:03.120
Fujimaki: ALL RIGHT, THEN.

00:18:04.920 --> 00:18:06.486
