Nanbu: UH, AND THE KID?

00:18:20.953 --> 00:18:22.620
WHAT'S GONNA HAPPEN
TO MY PARTNER?

00:18:22.620 --> 00:18:26.453
Fujimaki: THAT'S THE ACE
UP YOUR SLEEVE, HUH,

00:18:26.453 --> 00:18:30.153
