AS A SACRIFICIAL PAWN?

00:18:30.153 --> 00:18:32.886
YOU'VE FALLEN LOW,
HAVEN'T YOU, NANBU?

00:18:32.886 --> 00:18:35.386
( Nanbu stammers )

00:18:35.386 --> 00:18:36.920
( sighs )

00:18:38.253 --> 00:18:39.653
Fujimaki:
DON'T WORRY ABOUT HIM.

00:18:39.653 --> 00:18:43.553
WE'RE GOING TO BE PROFITING
OFF YOUR PARTNER UNTIL HE DIES,

00:18:43.553 --> 00:18:45.553
IN MY RING, OF COURSE.

00:18:45.553 --> 00:18:46.153
Nanbu: EH?

00:18:46.153 --> 00:18:49.853
Junk Dog: YEAH, DEAD SERIOUS.

00:18:49.853 --> 00:18:51.420
PLEASE GET ME IN HIS RING.

00:18:51.420 --> 00:18:54.620
Yuri: IF YOU'RE REALLY SERIOUS
ABOUT FIGHTING ME AGAIN,

00:18:54.620 --> 00:18:56.853
THEN YOU COME TO ME...

00:18:56.853 --> 00:18:58.320
IN MY RING.

00:18:59.453 --> 00:19:01.760
Nanbu: HE WANTS
TO GET TO HIS RING.

00:19:01.760 --> 00:19:03.293
( heart beating )

00:19:04.693 --> 00:19:06.326
NO WAY.

00:19:06.326 --> 00:19:10.460
MY PARTNER IS NOT GONNA
BE FIGHTING IN YOUR RING!

00:19:10.460 --> 00:19:11.960
( knife rattles )

00:19:11.960 --> 00:19:14.793
NEW PLAN!
I CAN PAY YOU BACK IN FULL

00:19:14.793 --> 00:19:16.293
ONCE HE WINS THIS TOURNAMENT.

