( Fujimaki chuckles )

00:19:27.326 --> 00:19:29.726
Junk Dog: SO YOU TOLD HIM
WHAT'S WHAT, RIGHT?

00:19:29.726 --> 00:19:30.893
HOW'D IT GO?

00:19:32.560 --> 00:19:36.193
YOU LISTENING?
I ASKED YOU A QUESTION, POPS.

00:19:36.193 --> 00:19:38.226
Nanbu: WOULD YOU JUST SHUT UP?

00:19:38.226 --> 00:19:40.593
I'M TRYING TO DO
SOME THINKIN' HERE, OKAY?

00:19:40.593 --> 00:19:41.593
STOP INTERRUPTING.

00:19:41.593 --> 00:19:42.360
Junk Dog: HMM.

00:19:44.893 --> 00:19:46.993
TELL ME WHAT HAPPENED.

00:19:46.993 --> 00:19:49.260
ARE WE OFF THE HOOK OR NOT?

00:19:52.026 --> 00:19:53.760
Nanbu: TIME FOR MEGALONIA.

00:19:53.760 --> 00:19:55.260
Junk Dog: EH?

00:19:56.860 --> 00:19:58.560
Nanbu: YOU HEARD ME.

00:19:58.560 --> 00:20:01.400
YOU'RE GETTING EXACTLY WHAT
YOU WANT, YOU LITTLE BASTARD.

00:20:01.400 --> 00:20:04.100
WE'VE GOTTA GET INTO MEGALONIA
NOW AND KICK ASS.

00:20:04.100 --> 00:20:05.766
THERE'S NO TURNING BACK NOW.

00:20:05.766 --> 00:20:07.133
( Junk Dog gasps )

00:20:07.133 --> 00:20:10.266
YOU MEAN I GET TO FIGHT YURI?

00:20:10.266 --> 00:20:12.533
Nanbu: YOU DON'T GET IT,
DO YOU?!

00:20:12.533 --> 00:20:16.033
WE ONLY HAVE THREE MONTHS
TO COME OUT ON TOP!

00:20:16.033 --> 00:20:18.433
IN ONLY THREE MONTHS TIME,

00:20:18.433 --> 00:20:20.933
WE DON'T JUST HAVE TO MAKE IT
INTO THE TOURNAMENT,

00:20:20.933 --> 00:20:23.033
WE HAVE TO WIN IT.

00:20:25.000 --> 00:20:27.400
( Junk Dog chuckles )

00:20:27.400 --> 00:20:28.800
Nanbu: EH?

00:20:28.800 --> 00:20:31.200
Junk Dog: NOT A PROBLEM.

00:20:32.933 --> 00:20:34.966
I DON'T INTEND TO LOSE AGAIN,

00:20:34.966 --> 00:20:37.200
NOT UNTIL I GET TO FIGHT YURI.

00:20:39.333 --> 00:20:40.100
Nanbu: EH...

00:20:50.666 --> 00:20:52.533
( tapping )

00:20:52.533 --> 00:20:55.200
( beeping )

00:20:57.966 --> 00:21:00.040
Man: MAN, POOR GUY.

