( chews )
A FEW PAYMENTS LATE,

00:21:02.340 --> 00:21:05.440
AND BAM, HE'S CHOPPED APART,
ORGANS ALL SOLD OFF.

00:21:05.440 --> 00:21:08.573
NOW HIS WHOLE IDENTITY
IS ABOUT TO BE OVERWRITTEN.

00:21:08.573 --> 00:21:11.273
Fujimaki: THIS IS ALL THE HELP
YOU'LL GET FROM ME.

00:21:11.273 --> 00:21:14.540
EVERYTHING ELSE
IS UP TO THE TWO OF YOU.

00:21:14.540 --> 00:21:16.606
YOU GOT THAT, NANBU?

00:21:16.606 --> 00:21:18.140
( beeping )

00:21:19.073 --> 00:21:21.173
YOU CAN'T BE SERIOUS.

00:21:21.173 --> 00:21:24.240
WHAT CAN A COUPLE OF FRAUDS
HOPE TO DO?

00:21:24.240 --> 00:21:27.206
Nanbu: I'VE GOT ONE HELL
OF A PLAN FOR THIS.

00:21:27.206 --> 00:21:30.106
WE'RE GONNA WIN IT. ( grunts )

00:21:31.873 --> 00:21:34.173
I KNOW HOW TO HANDLE THINGS.

00:21:34.173 --> 00:21:36.540
I'VE BEEN BETTING ON BLUFFS
MY WHOLE DAMN LIFE.

00:21:36.540 --> 00:21:38.540
SO WHAT CAN FRAUDS DO?

00:21:38.540 --> 00:21:42.073
I'M GONNA SHOW YOU
EXACTLY WHAT WE CAN DO!

00:21:44.340 --> 00:21:44.940
( beeps )

00:21:44.940 --> 00:21:46.140
Man: THERE WE GO.

00:21:46.140 --> 00:21:48.206
NOW ALL WE NEED IS A NEW NAME,

00:21:48.206 --> 00:21:51.340
AND WE'LL HAVE
A FRESHLY MINTED CITIZEN.

00:21:51.340 --> 00:21:52.840
HMM?

00:21:53.973 --> 00:21:55.873
( Nanbu shudders )

00:21:55.873 --> 00:21:59.046
IT'S YOUR NAME. YOU PICK IT.

